{"tid":2358663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"儲水式熱水爐苦主留言專區","createTime":"2021-01-08T09:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T09:56:56.000Z","uid":374394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7da43487599f3f0dfce52ca218cc727dbe6b1d7","tid":2358663,"uid":374394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:52:03.000Z","msg":"事緣係咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日得嗰5度，出完街返到屋企諗住沖個涼<br />\n而小弟屋企個菲傭十分之鍾情於用熱水洗碗<br />\n咁我喺沖涼前已經用英文同佢講<br />\n&ldquo; <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">for safety reason please leave the kitchen until I finish the shower thank you</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rdquo;<br />\n咁佢就話OK<br />\n我入到廁所<br />\n即刻用9秒九嘅時間沖濕個身然後落梘<br />\n係我捽緊胳肋底嘅時候<br />\n我聽到！<br />\n我聽到廚房有水聲<br />\n但係已經太遲了<br />\n喺我再開花灑嘅時候啲熱水已經俾佢<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">用撚晒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58440238e55cee8a8ca2a6a2b7bc2899160fac61","tid":2358663,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"61fa92eb63e54f3f1f662089302545a214fcc2c4","tid":2358663,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"4／10"}]}